{"title":"空军诗情","authors":["周鹤　温民法"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":9,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"空军诗情〔二首〕\t周鹤　温民法"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细如线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色机场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂银帘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青的鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒雨苦练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟随师长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草坪上作表演："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横滚、翻腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掠过机场镜中天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绞乱了一天雨线……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨过天晴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乳白的云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镶金边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师长伫立起飞线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对对鹰雏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比翼入蓝天……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦炮弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军械员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦弹忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用心用汗用阳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日擦千颗不嫌多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦亮炮弹擦弹舱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀里抱炮弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿掂份量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗炮弹有多重？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级仇恨里边装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦呀擦，想呀想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一遍一遍记心上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗炮弹一把火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑道火墙拦豺狼……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军械员，擦弹忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用心用汗用阳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹越擦越洁净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿越擦越亮堂。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}